    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294130/extras/748564362797c60281bf419995e52fac.avif?t=1766587856\" width=1045 height=277 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Climb. Fall. Rise again.</strong><br><br>In <i>Death Trap Mountain</i>, every jump counts. Set in the mysterious world of <strong>Holomundran</strong>, you play as <strong>Mitch</strong>, an ordinary adventurer on an impossible mission—to rescue his blue-furred dog, <strong>Gil</strong>, from the clutches of <strong>Xelthorak</strong>, an ancient dragon who believes devouring Gil’s experimental energy will grant him limitless power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To reach the dragon’s lair, you must ascend <strong>Death Trap Mountain</strong>—a brutal vertical labyrinth filled with collapsing ledges, spinning blades, and gravity-defying puzzles. Every mistake sends you tumbling back down, but every climb teaches you something new.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294130/extras/cbaee77bed915369e59de9cd5e49aa55.webp?t=1766587856\" width=13 height=14 /></span>  <strong>Precision Platforming:</strong> Tight, responsive controls built for skill-based gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294130/extras/cbaee77bed915369e59de9cd5e49aa55.webp?t=1766587856\" width=13 height=14 /></span>  <strong>Evolving Challenges:</strong> Dynamic traps, puzzles, enemies and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294130/extras/cbaee77bed915369e59de9cd5e49aa55.webp?t=1766587856\" width=13 height=14 /></span>  <strong>A Heartfelt Quest:</strong> Save Gil, your one true companion, from Xelthorak’s hunger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294130/extras/cbaee77bed915369e59de9cd5e49aa55.webp?t=1766587856\" width=13 height=14 /></span>  <strong>Atmospheric World:</strong> Handcrafted levels and that make gameplay unforgettable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294130/extras/cbaee77bed915369e59de9cd5e49aa55.webp?t=1766587856\" width=13 height=14 /></span>  <strong>Easy to learn, hard to master</strong>: Perfect for fans of <i>Jump King</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you conquer <strong>Death Trap Mountain</strong> and rescue <strong>Gil</strong> before <strong>Xelthorak</strong> unleashes his fury on Holomundran?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
